/*
  Simple caching headers for generic static hosts or Netlify/Vercel if applicable.
  For GitHub Pages, this file (_headers) does not work natively but is good practice if moving to Netlify/Vercel later as suggested in the plan.
  The 'Versioned CSS' strategy we implemented (styles.v1.css) handles the cache breaking for GitHub Pages.
*/
/*.css
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=31536000, immutable

/*.js
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=31536000, immutable

/*.woff2
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=31536000, immutable
